#!new # vim:syntax=sh:tw=72

# REQUIREMENTS & DEFAULTS
--default VERS=0.0
--default AUTHOR=David C Black
--default EMAIL=dcblack@mac.com

# BRIEF
#! Creates a simple SystemC project that uses cmake

=pod

=head1 NAME

B<cpp-cmake template> - Creates a simple SystemC project

=head1 SYNOPSIS

B<new> sc-project I<OPTIONS> {:I<NAME>:}

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Creates a basic directory to build a simple SystemC project.

    NAME/
    ├── CMakeLists.txt
    ├── cmake
    │   ├── policy.cmake
    │   └── project_defaults.cmake
    ├── main.cpp
    ├── NAME.hpp
    └── NAME.cpp

=head1 PARAMETERS

=over

=item AUTHOR

=item COMPANY

=item EMAIL

=item VERS

Version number #.# (defaults to 0.0)

=back

=head1 REQUIREMENTS

An appropriate version of cmake version 3.21 or better should be installed.

